-- City Developments Q2 core profit up 90 pct
-- By Rachel Armstrong
-- Wed Aug 13, 2014 08:14PM EDT
-- None



SINGAPORE, Aug 14 (Reuters) - City Developments Ltd <CTDM.SI>, Southeast Asia's second-largest property developer, reported a 90 percent rise in its second quarter core net profit on Thursday, led by its hotel and property development businesses.

It said core earnings came in at S$138 million ($110.5 million)compared with S$73 million a year ago.